set

public void set(double speed,
                byte syncGroup)
Never call this method. We need to have one in order to implement the SpeedController interface and pass this class into a DriveTrain, etc., but we are using Victors which do not use syncGroups.

Specified by:
set in interface edu.wpi.first.wpilibj.SpeedController
Parameters:
speed - The speed to set. Value should be between -1.0 and 1.0.
syncGroup - The update group to add this Set() to, pending UpdateSyncGroup(). If 0, update immediately.
